A MAN suffered serious facial injuries when he was attacked with a bottle in Glasgow. Man injured in city street bottle attack A MAN suffered serious facial injuries when he was attacked with a bottle in Glasgow.The 31-year-old victim was attacked by a man as he walked down a street in the Ballieston area at 9pm on Wednesday.The man was struck with the bottle during the incident in South Scott Street and suffered serious wounds to his face.Police appealed for witnesses to come forward. 